data.description: The Malvern from our Watermill Collection features 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. Guests are greeted by a lovely foyer that overs up to the main living area. The kitchen features beautiful granite countertops overlooking the family room. The master suite is nestled in the corner of the home for optimum privacy and boasts a private master bath and walk-in closet. A two-car garage completes this beautiful home. Estimated availability Oct 2020!
